<article id="donate" class="slate">
	<div class="container">
		<h1 class="article-header"><i class="fa fa-heart"></i> Donate</h1>
		<p>We are not maintained by large communities, rather, a few individuals maintain the Cyan.TF infrastructure. We are independent and don't have as much support as the big wig community leaders and this is where donations come in.</p>
		<p>By donating, you show your support for Cyan.TF and help us pay for the various costs to keep your favorite server alive and kicking. But that isn't all&hellip;</p><p>As a thank you from us, you will receive special perks in the server! The list below shows all perks you get for donating.<sup><b>*</b></sup></p>
		<ul>
			<li>Special <b style="color:#4CBA5B;">[Donor]</b> tag and chat color</li>
			<li>Reserved slot</li>
			<li>Halloween footprints</li>
			<li>Voice menu effects</li>
			<li>Noisemaker</li>
			<li>Better RTD good roll chance</li>
			<li>Resize your own head</li>
			<li>Resize yourself (damage dealt reduced if smaller)</li>
			<li>Set your killstreak amount</li>
			<li>Autobalance immunity</li>
			<li>Flaming Huntsman arrows</li>
			<li>Ping limit immunity</li>
			<li>Sparkle trail</li>
			<li>Rocket yourself</li>
			<li>Projectile particle effects changer</li>
			<li>Shapeshift (change to any class from anywhere)</li>
			<li>Drive a bumper car</li>
			<li>Increased saysound limit per round and shorter cooldown</li>
			<li>Add a rainbow glow to yourself</li>
			<li>And more to come!</li>
		</ul>

		<p>Donor perks are not permanent and will expire. However, you get longer donor perks the more you donate. $5 gets you 31 days of donor perks, $10 gets you 62 and so on. When your perks expire, you will not be charged but you will need to donate again to get perks back. If you donate while your perks are already active then you will extend your donor time.</p>

		<span class="horizontal-divider"></span>

		<p class="text-center">When you are ready to donate, choose your method of donation by clicking one of the buttons below.</p>
		<div class="row top-large-margin bottom-large-margin">
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<a href="#donate-with-cash" data-toggle="collapse" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl btn-block" role="button">Donate with Cash</a>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<a href="#donate-with-items" data-toggle="collapse" class="btn btn-primary btn-xl btn-block" role="button">Donate with Items</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div id="donate-with-items" class="collapse row">
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<div class="widget widget-summary widget-light">
					<div class="summary-title">Trade via Steam</div>
					<div class="summary-light summary-padded">
						<p>All item donations are handled by <b>depthbomb</b>. To donate items simply send a trade offer using the button to the right and you will be manually added to the system after the items have been accepted.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<div class="widget widget-summary widget-light">
					<div class="summary-title">Accepted Items</div>
					<div class="summary-light summary-padded">
						<div class="row items-container">
							<div class="col-sm-2">
								<div class="item item-unique" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" title="Mann Co. Supply Crate Key" data-content="This item is valued at $2.50. Two are needed for minimum donation amount.">
									<img class="item-image" src="https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/apps/440/icons/key.067945a6cae528464e4fa00126f0ef17ee2dc8b5.png">
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-sm-2">
								<div class="item item-unique" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" title="Tour of Duty Ticket" data-content="This item is valued at $1.00. Five are needed for minimum donation amount.">
									<img class="item-image" src="https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/apps/440/icons/mvm_ticket.09ace67431a4605c3ddc8593d62ccf957f65aeeb.png">
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-sm-2">
								<div class="item item-unique" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" title="Squad Surplus Voucher" data-content="This item is valued at $2.00. Three are needed for minimum donation amount (plus extra time).">
									<img class="item-image" src="https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/apps/440/icons/mvm_squad_surplus.016b1bd4ea8a12eb7d7ecf278f0d60ae6424cdda.png">
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-sm-2">
								<div class="item item-unusual" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" title="Unusual Items" data-content="Your donor perk duration will vary depending on the value of the item.">
									<img class="item-image" src="{URL}/assets/img/items/item_unknown.png">
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<a href="{_re('https://steamcommunity.com/tradeoffer/new/?partner=66133073&token=cFIlCTRq')}" class="btn btn-success btn-block" target="_blank"><span class="fa fa-exchange"></span> Send a Trade Offer</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div id="donate-with-cash" class="collapse">
			<div class="widget widget-summary widget-light">
				<div class="summary-title">Donate with Cash</div>
				<div class="summary-light summary-padded">
					<p>All cash donations are handled exclusively with PayPal. This system is completely automated so you will receive your donor perks in 15 to 45 minutes after the transaction has been completed.</p>
					<a href="{URL}/donor" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block">Donate</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="text-center top-small-margin no-bottom-margin">
			<p class="text-info lead">Donating $100 or more in one transaction, be it cash or items, will get you Hyper Donor and your perks never expire!</p>
		</div>

	</div>
</article>
